---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Typescript, Python, Openjdk, Kotlin, Go, React, Solid, Astro as AstroIcon, Tailwindcss, Nextdotjs, Nodedotjs, Postgresql, Git, Docker, Linux } from "simple-icons-astro";
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pb-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold pb-4 text-cyan-12">About</h1>
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold pb-2 text-cyan-11">
      Software Engineer
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg">
      I build robust, scalable full-stack applications with a focus on clean
      architecture and exceptional user experiences.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Photo Placeholder (hidden for now, ready for future implementation) -->
  <div class="hidden pb-8" id="photo-placeholder">
    <!-- Photo will go here -->
  </div>

  <!-- Background Section -->
  <section class="pb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold pb-4">Background</h2>
    <p class="pb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      I'm a software engineer from Indonesia with a passion for building
      full-stack applications that solve real problems. My journey into software
      development began with a curiosity about how things work, which evolved
      into a deep commitment to crafting well-designed, maintainable systems.
    </p>
    <p class="pb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      Throughout my career, I've worked across the entire stack, from designing
      responsive user interfaces to architecting backend services and managing
      infrastructure. I thrive in environments where I can take ownership of
      projects from concept to deployment, ensuring quality at every layer.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
      What drives my work is the intersection of technical excellence and
      practical impact. I believe great software is not just about writing code,
      but about understanding user needs, making thoughtful architectural
      decisions, and building systems that are both powerful and maintainable.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Technical Expertise Section -->
  <section class="pb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold pb-4">Technical Expertise</h2>
    
    <!-- Problem Domains -->
    <div class="pb-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pb-3 text-cyan-11">Problem Domains</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <li class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-slate-6">
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-12">Full-Stack Web Applications:</span>
          <span class="text-slate-11"> Building end-to-end web solutions with modern frameworks, from responsive frontends to scalable backend APIs.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-slate-6">
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-12">API Design & Development:</span>
          <span class="text-slate-11"> Designing and implementing RESTful and GraphQL APIs with a focus on performance, security, and developer experience.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-slate-6">
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-12">Database Architecture:</span>
          <span class="text-slate-11"> Designing efficient data models and optimizing queries for both relational and NoSQL databases.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-slate-6">
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-12">DevOps & Infrastructure:</span>
          <span class="text-slate-11"> Containerization, CI/CD pipelines, and cloud deployment strategies for reliable, automated workflows.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Development Approach -->
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pb-3 text-cyan-11">Development Approach</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <li class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-cyan-6">
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-12">Code Quality:</span>
          <span class="text-slate-11"> Writing clean, testable, and well-documented code that prioritizes maintainability and readability.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-cyan-6">
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-12">Performance Optimization:</span>
          <span class="text-slate-11"> Profiling and optimizing applications for speed, efficiency, and scalability.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-cyan-6">
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-12">User-Centric Design:</span>
          <span class="text-slate-11"> Building interfaces and experiences that are intuitive, accessible, and delightful to use.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="pl-4 border-l-2 border-cyan-6">
          <span class="font-semibold text-slate-12">Continuous Learning:</span>
          <span class="text-slate-11"> Staying current with emerging technologies and best practices in the rapidly evolving software landscape.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Skills & Technologies Section -->
  <section class="pb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold pb-4">Skills & Technologies</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pb-2 text-cyan-11">Languages</h3>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-3 text-slate-11 rounded-md text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <Typescript class="w-4 h-4" />
            TypeScript
          </span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-3 text-slate-11 rounded-md text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <Python class="w-4 h-4" />
            Python
          </span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-3 text-slate-11 rounded-md text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <Openjdk class="w-4 h-4" />
            Java
          </span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-3 text-slate-11 rounded-md text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <Kotlin class="w-4 h-4" />
            Kotlin
          </span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-3 text-slate-11 rounded-md text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <Go class="w-4 h-4" />
            Go
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pb-2 text-cyan-11">Frontend</h3>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-3 text-slate-11 rounded-md text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <React class="w-4 h-4" />
            React
          </span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-3 text-slate-11 rounded-md text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <Solid class="w-4 h-4" />
            Solid
          </span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-3 text-slate-11 rounded-md text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <AstroIcon class="w-4 h-4" />
            Astro
          </span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-3 text-slate-11 rounded-md text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <Tailwindcss class="w-4 h-4" />
            Tailwind CSS
          </span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-3 text-slate-11 rounded-md text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <Nextdotjs class="w-4 h-4" />
            Next.js
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pb-2 text-cyan-11">Backend</h3>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-3 text-slate-11 rounded-md text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <Nodedotjs class="w-4 h-4" />
            Node.js
          </span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-3 text-slate-11 rounded-md text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <Postgresql class="w-4 h-4" />
            PostgreSQL
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pb-2 text-cyan-11">Tools</h3>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-3 text-slate-11 rounded-md text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <Git class="w-4 h-4" />
            Git
          </span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-3 text-slate-11 rounded-md text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <Docker class="w-4 h-4" />
            Docker
          </span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-3 text-slate-11 rounded-md text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <Linux class="w-4 h-4" />
            Linux
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Current Focus Section -->
  <section class="pb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold pb-4">Current Focus</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pb-2 text-cyan-11">What I'm Building</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-11">
          Currently focused on developing modern web applications using React,
          TypeScript, and Node.js. I'm particularly interested in creating
          developer tools and platforms that improve workflow efficiency and
          code quality.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pb-2 text-cyan-11">What I'm Learning</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-11">
          Exploring advanced patterns in distributed systems, diving deeper into
          performance optimization techniques, and experimenting with emerging
          frontend frameworks like Solid and Astro. Also expanding my knowledge
          in system design and cloud-native architectures.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold pb-2 text-cyan-11">Future Interests</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-11">
          Interested in contributing to open-source projects, exploring
          WebAssembly for performance-critical applications, and building tools
          that help developers ship better software faster. Always looking for
          opportunities to work on challenging problems with talented teams.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Connect Section -->
  <section class="pb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold pb-4">Let's Connect</h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed pb-4">
      I'm always open to discussing new opportunities, collaborations, or
      interesting technical challenges. Feel free to reach out if you'd like to
      work together or just chat about technology.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a
        href="https://github.com/yourusername"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-cyan-11 hover:text-cyan-12 underline"
      >
        GitHub
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourusername"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-cyan-11 hover:text-cyan-12 underline"
      >
        LinkedIn
      </a>
      <a
        href="mailto:your.email@example.com"
        class="text-cyan-11 hover:text-cyan-12 underline"
      >
        Email
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
